        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued September 8 at 5:33PM CDT until September 8 at 5:45PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 532 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Dalhart, moving
southeast at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and half dollar size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Dalhart.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
